A team agreement was created to define working norms, responsibilities, and collaboration rules for the development of the Smart Queue Management System for Banks. This agreement ensures smooth teamwork, accountability, and effective communication throughout the project lifecycle.
Team Working Norms
•	All team members will actively participate in project-related activities.
•	Tasks will be distributed equally among team members.
•	Regular discussions will be conducted to track progress.
•	All decisions will be made collectively by the team.
•	Any issues or conflicts will be resolved through mutual discussion.
Communication Guidelines
•	Team members will communicate through regular meetings and online platforms.
•	Important updates and changes will be shared with all members.
•	Deadlines will be respected and followed strictly.
Quality and Responsibility Agreement
•	Each member is responsible for completing assigned tasks on time.
•	Work submitted by any member will be reviewed by at least one other member.
•	The team agrees to maintain academic honesty and originality.
This team agreement was accepted by all members to ensure disciplined, collaborative, and efficient project execution.
